Title: Data compression
Description: There is a very high possibility that your browser downloaded this website as compressed data. I can feel sure saying this because the web standard defines gzip as a standard compressor for web content. So what it achieved by compressing this webpage? As with any data compression algorithm, it reduces the data’s size with no or very little data loss. Data compression is a bigger deal than you might imagine, some works conclude that compression is equal to intelligence.
